OL,3,CFather, 82, dies after broken back
OL,4,Cleft undiagnosed for 16 days
OL,6,FA man from Pembrokeshire says he is
OL,7,F"angry" after his father died from a
OL,8,Fbroken back, 16 days after being sent
OL,9,Fhome from Withybush Hospital.
OL,11,FDavid Wilson's father Harry, 82, had
OL,12,Fbeen living independently but had a
OL,13,Ffall at home. He was taken to A&E,
OL,14,Fwhere after being examined and x-rayed
OL,15,Fhe was taken to the frailty unit.
OL,17,FAfter a few days he was discharged,
OL,18,Fdespite still complaining of a lot of
OL,19,Fpain.
