OL,3,CFather, 82, dies after broken back
OL,4,Cleft undiagnosed for 16 days
OL,6,FDavid described his father as being
OL,7,F"in agony" and unable to walk into the
OL,8,Fhome. He said his father sat in a
OL,9,Fchair for five days and nights because
OL,10,Fof the pain.
OL,12,FIt was only after a physiotherapist
OL,13,Fcame to examine him that the family
OL,14,Fcalled an ambulance again and Harry
OL,15,Fwas re-admitted to hospital.
OL,17,FAfter eight days back in hospital,
OL,18,FDavid claims his dad's original x-ray
OL,19,Fwas re-examined and showed that he had
OL,20,Fbroken his back weeks earlier - before
OL,21,Fhe had first attended hospital.
