OL,6,FHe was urgently taken to Morriston
OL,7,FHospital in Swansea for surgery but it
OL,8,Fwas then that he contracted pneumonia
OL,9,Fand died on 18 July, exactly a month
OL,10,Fafter his fall.
OL,12,FDavid said his father "died in pain
OL,13,Fand angry, which was unusual because
OL,14,Fhe wasn't an angry man, but he
OL,15,Frealised that he'd been very badly let
OL,16,Fdown".
OL,18,FHe also described his own feelings of
OL,19,F"anger" saying, "it's a shame because
OL,20,Fmy dad was a lovely man so to feel
OL,21,Fanger at his death, it's awful".
