OL,6,FHe said: "The response from Hywel Dda
OL,7,FUniversity Health Board has been
OL,8,Fabominable, it took 18 months for an
OL,9,Fofficial letter of response. It makes
OL,10,Fyou feel sick to the pit of your
OL,11,Fstomach that they haven't even got the
OL,12,Fdecency to put their hands up and say
OL,13,F'yeah we messed up big time.'"
OL,15,F"That delay killed him, it was a
OL,16,Fwholly avoidable death.
