OL,6,F"I appreciate that doctors and nurses
OL,7,Fare human beings and make mistakes. If
OL,8,FHywel Dda said 'one of our staff made
OL,9,Fa dreadful mistake we are sorry', I'm
OL,10,Fnot saying we'd be happy but at least
OL,11,Fthey would've acknowledged it, but
OL,12,Fit's the wriggling that really gets on
OL,13,Fmy nerves, the attempt to get off the
OL,14,Fhook."
OL,16,FSharon Daniel Director of Nursing,
OL,17,FQuality & Patient Experience at Hywel
OL,18,FDda University Health Board said: "We
OL,19,Fextend our deepest sympathies to the
OL,20,Ffamily who continue to deal with their
OL,21,Floss.
