OL,6,F"To protect patient privacy, we cannot
OL,7,Fcomment on individual cases. We take
OL,8,Fcomplaints about care given to
OL,9,Fpatients under our care very seriously
OL,10,Fand have robust processes in place to
OL,11,Finvestigate complaints, identifying
OL,12,Fany issues and, where appropriate,
OL,13,Fputting improvements in place to
OL,14,Fprevent such an occurrence in the
OL,15,Ffuture.
OL,17,F"We always try to engage with those
OL,18,Fdirectly impacted whenever there is
OL,19,Fcause for concern and to work together
OL,20,Fto resolve the complaint."
